title: Je Suis Yahabibi
itunes:title: Je Suis Yahabibi
description: Jackie is back from Paris and breaks down her trip including the time she lost the opportunity to be a Princess and get a Birkin bag, pays homage to Leonardo Dicaprio and how to cast a love spell with period blood. The range!
